<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, July 5 (Xinhua) -- Greece said Monday that 512 Albanian
illegal immigrants had been arrested in the northwestern Greek
region of Epirus over the past three days in a nationwide
crackdown on illegal immigrants.
</P>
